{"tid":2267582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國有學生因為見到香港反送中運動而設計防TG口罩獲設計銅獎","createTime":"2020-11-02T07:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T14:50:21.000Z","uid":22556,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6d6caa88e8a2498da1d0c765bce4fa7e8050df1b","tid":2267582,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:38:52.000Z","msg":"四名嚟自美國維吉尼亞理工學院暨州立大學嘅學生，透過佢哋設計嘅口罩、喺傑出工業設計獎學生設計項目中贏得銅獎。<br />\n<br />\n研發團隊將呢款口罩命名為Temporary Eye and Respiratory Mask、簡稱T.E.A.R，可以摺疊收藏、方便攜帶，並且能夠抵擋催淚彈15分鐘。佢哋表示，口罩概念源於上年反送中運動當中、無懼催淚彈嘅香港抗爭者。希望透過呢個口罩、引起大眾對濫用催淚彈嘅關注，捍衛言論自由、以及公民應有抗議嘅權利。<br />\n<br />\n上年反送中運動期間，警方曾經發射超過16000枚催淚彈，彭博社曾經引述警方數字、指88%港人曾經曝露喺催淚氣體之下。雖然催淚彈暫別街頭，但香港人遊行集會示威權利，都被政府以防疫為由抗絕。縱使當局壓得住抗議行動，但世界都會記得無畏無懼嘅香港人。<br />\n<br />\n但願呢個口罩，喺香港以至世界，都唔會有用得著嘅一日。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/273813022746352/posts/3332071523587138/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F273813022746352%2Fposts%2F3332071523587138%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=6c9b7829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/273813022746352/posts/3332071523587138/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"16590357de40ab8da183d65a7802de6e7b71c1ec","tid":2267582,"uid":49329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a94d507381d2c7e4101d0d70d662e15106ee3d","tid":2267582,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:26:04.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"5270a23678a9a79ac28bc64d9acd674806df649c","tid":2267582,"uid